NNQT_istance: Which are the books that have a known publication date, written by a militarypersons born before 1800?
correct_NNQT_istance: Which are the books that have a known publication date, written by a military person born before 1800?
query:
SELECT DISTINCT ?work WHERE { ?work dbo:author ?auth;   rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Book>.
	?auth a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/MilitaryPerson>.
	?auth dbo:birthDate ?bDate.
	FILTER(?bDate < "1800-01-01"^^xsd:date).
	OPTIONAL{{?work dbp:releaseDate ?date} UNION {?work dbo:publicationDate ?date} UNION {?work dbo:pubDate ?date}}   FILTER(Bound(?date))}
